---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Team Leaders — Departure: Fitness Quest"
  description="Teams in Departure elect their own Team Leader every two months. Earn a +10% XP boost, a signing bonus, and the power to lead the warpath. Real democracy for real teams."
  ogImage="/social/team-leader.jpg"
>
  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="pt-16 pb-12 lg:pt-24 lg:pb-16">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 text-center">
      <span class="text-gold text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider">The Team Leader System</span>
      <h1 class="text-4xl sm:text-6xl font-extrabold mt-3 mb-4">Lead the warband.</h1>
      <p class="text-text-muted text-lg max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        Every great team has someone who sets the pace. In Departure, that person is chosen by the team —
        and gets paid for it.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Why it exists -->
  <section class="py-16 bg-surface/30">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6">
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
        <div>
          <span class="text-primary-light text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider">Why it matters</span>
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mt-2 mb-4">Fitness teams need leaders.</h2>
          <p class="text-text-muted mb-4">
            Most team fitness apps give every member the same buttons and hope someone steps up.
            Nobody does. The group chat goes quiet, the streak dies, and everyone drifts.
          </p>
          <p class="text-text-muted">
            Departure solves that with a real role: one Team Leader, elected by the team, with exclusive
            responsibilities and a reward worth earning.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-surface rounded-2xl p-6 border border-gold/30">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4">
            <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-gold/15 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-gold" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20"><path d="M5 3a2 2 0 00-2 2v2a2 2 0 002 2h.5a.5.5 0 010 1H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v2a2 2 0 002 2h10a2 2 0 002-2v-2a2 2 0 00-2-2h-.5a.5.5 0 010-1h.5a2 2 0 002-2V5a2 2 0 00-2-2H5z"/></svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold">The Rewards</h3>
          </div>
          <ul class="space-y-3 text-sm">
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <span class="text-gold font-bold shrink-0">+10%</span>
              <span class="text-text-muted">XP on every workout for the entire 2-month term. Stacks with Starter/Elite and active boosts up to a 5× cap.</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <span class="text-green font-bold shrink-0">Coins</span>
              <span class="text-text-muted">Signing bonus of 1,000 + 100 × team size. Bigger team = bigger payout.</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <span class="text-gold font-bold shrink-0">Crown</span>
              <span class="text-text-muted">Gold ribbon displayed on your profile and the team page for your whole term.</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <span class="text-blue-400 font-bold shrink-0">Override</span>
              <span class="text-text-muted">Restore XP on a teammate's flagged workout if the anti-cheat system got it wrong. 25 coins per use, fully logged.</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Responsibilities -->
  <section class="py-16">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6">
      <div class="text-center mb-12">
        <span class="text-primary-light text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider">The Job</span>
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mt-2">What a leader actually does.</h2>
        <p class="text-text-muted mt-3 max-w-2xl mx-auto">The perks aren't free. Being elected means showing up.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
        <div class="bg-surface rounded-2xl p-6 border border-white/5">
          <div class="text-2xl mb-3">⚔️</div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold mb-2">Advance the warpath</h3>
          <p class="text-text-muted text-sm">Only the Team Leader can trigger monster battles. The team's journey forward depends on you showing up and pulling the trigger.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-surface rounded-2xl p-6 border border-white/5">
          <div class="text-2xl mb-3">💬</div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold mb-2">Run the feed</h3>
          <p class="text-text-muted text-sm">React, comment, encourage. Your activity is public — and voted on when your term ends.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-surface rounded-2xl p-6 border border-white/5">
          <div class="text-2xl mb-3">🤝</div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold mb-2">Recruit warriors</h3>
          <p class="text-text-muted text-sm">A bigger team means a bigger signing bonus for whoever the team elects next. Grow the warband.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-surface rounded-2xl p-6 border border-white/5">
          <div class="text-2xl mb-3">🛡️</div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold mb-2">Override fair fails</h3>
          <p class="text-text-muted text-sm">Anti-cheat is aggressive on purpose. When it flags an honest workout, the leader can restore it. Every override is logged for team transparency.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Elections -->
  <section class="py-16 bg-surface/30">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6">
      <div class="text-center mb-12">
        <span class="text-gold text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider">Elections</span>
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mt-2">Every 60 days. Every member votes.</h2>
        <p class="text-text-muted mt-3 max-w-2xl mx-auto">A one-week window. A 280-character platform statement. One vote per member. Plurality wins.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-4">
        <div class="bg-surface rounded-2xl p-5 border border-white/5">
          <div class="w-8 h-8 bg-primary/20 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mb-3">
            <span class="text-primary-light text-sm font-bold">1</span>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-bold mb-1">Nominations</h3>
          <p class="text-text-muted text-xs">3 days. Self-nominate or nominate a teammate.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-surface rounded-2xl p-5 border border-white/5">
          <div class="w-8 h-8 bg-primary/20 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mb-3">
            <span class="text-primary-light text-sm font-bold">2</span>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-bold mb-1">Campaign</h3>
          <p class="text-text-muted text-xs">3 days. Each candidate shares a 280-character pitch.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-surface rounded-2xl p-5 border border-white/5">
          <div class="w-8 h-8 bg-primary/20 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mb-3">
            <span class="text-primary-light text-sm font-bold">3</span>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-bold mb-1">Vote</h3>
          <p class="text-text-muted text-xs">1 day. One vote per member. Plurality wins.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-surface rounded-2xl p-5 border border-gold/30">
          <div class="w-8 h-8 bg-gold/15 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mb-3">
            <span class="text-gold text-sm font-bold">4</span>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-bold mb-1">Coronation</h3>
          <p class="text-text-muted text-xs">New leader announced. Bonus + XP boost activate for 60 days.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <p class="text-center text-text-muted text-xs mt-6">
        Elections require at least 3 team members. Smaller teams ride with the Steward until they grow.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Steward -->
  <section class="py-16">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6">
      <div class="bg-surface rounded-2xl p-8 border border-slate-500/20">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4">
          <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-slate-500/15 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-slate-300" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20"><path d="M5 3a2 2 0 00-2 2v2a2 2 0 002 2h.5a.5.5 0 010 1H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v2a2 2 0 002 2h10a2 2 0 002-2v-2a2 2 0 00-2-2h-.5a.5.5 0 010-1h.5a2 2 0 002-2V5a2 2 0 00-2-2H5z"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold">The Steward</h3>
        </div>
        <p class="text-text-muted mb-3">
          Created a team? You start as the Steward — not the Team Leader. You do the work: warpath, overrides, recruitment.
          But the rewards only land if the team votes you in.
        </p>
        <p class="text-text-muted">
          Lead by example. Earn the crown.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Accountability -->
  <section class="py-16 bg-surface/30">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6">
      <div class="text-center mb-10">
        <span class="text-blue-400 text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider">Accountability</span>
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mt-2">Transparent by design.</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
        <div class="bg-surface rounded-2xl p-6 border border-white/5">
          <h3 class="font-bold mb-2">Every override logged</h3>
          <p class="text-text-muted text-sm">Any XP restoration is visible to every team member, with who did it, when, and why.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-surface rounded-2xl p-6 border border-white/5">
          <h3 class="font-bold mb-2">Recall anytime</h3>
          <p class="text-text-muted text-sm">If the leader goes inactive for 14+ days, members can initiate a recall petition. Simple majority ends the term.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-surface rounded-2xl p-6 border border-white/5">
          <h3 class="font-bold mb-2">Resign freely</h3>
          <p class="text-text-muted text-sm">Not feeling it? Step down. Your XP boost deactivates immediately and the team runs an early election.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <section class="py-20">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 text-center">
      <h2 class="text-4xl font-extrabold mb-4">Earn the crown.</h2>
      <p class="text-text-muted text-lg mb-8">
        Join a team. Show up. Get elected. Lead the warband for 60 days.
      </p>
      <a href="/" class="inline-block bg-gradient-to-r from-primary to-primary-light text-white font-bold py-3 px-8 rounded-full hover:opacity-90 transition">
        Download Departure
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
